  <brief_title>Prevention of Post-traumatic Seizures With Levetiracetam</brief_title>
  <acronym>TRACK</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind Study Assessing the Effects of Levetiracetam Compared to Placebo in the Prevention of Early Epileptic Seizures and Late Epilepsy in Patients With Severe Traumatic Brain Injury</official_title>
